<h2 class="bold font-l">Barbatos Doesn't Give Up Yet.</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Despite being half-dead, down one arm, and falling apart: Mikazuki Augus and ASW-G-08 Gundam Barbatos Lupus Rex reminds the soldiers of Gjallarhorn one last time why he is known as &quot;The Devil of Tekkadan&quot;. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MookHorrorShow" class='trope-example-link'>Mook Horror Show</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="fkavjj" data-video-descrip="After being gunned down while trying to protect Ride from assassins sent by Nobliss Gordon, Orga Itsuka accepts his death and issues one last order to the members of Tekkadan: to keep going forwards and that he will be waiting for them at the end of their own roads." data-video-title="Orga Itsuka" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/fkavjj_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/fkavjj.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/FaceDeathWithDignity" data-video-tropename="Face Death with Dignity" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Anime/MobileSuitGundamIronBloodedOrphans" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/fkavjj.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Orga Itsuka</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="qqxf23" data-video-descrip="After spending all of Season 2 knowingly and unknowingly causing problems and killing people left-and-right because of his actions, it is satisfying to see Iok Kujan getting crushed to death by Akihiro." data-video-title="Iok Kujan" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/qqxf23_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/screen_shot_2020_10_01_at_124212_pm.png" data-video-trope="Main/AssholeVictim" data-video-tropename="Asshole Victim" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Anime/MobileSuitGundamIronBloodedOrphans" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/screen_shot_2020_10_01_at_124212_pm.png">
<p><span class="bold">Iok Kujan</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="t46vg6" data-video-descrip="Mika runs on this trope with all cylinders. There is no place for Honor on the battlefield like what Carta expected. Did you really think that you're in the Pokemon Universe?" data-video-title="Mikazuki Augus" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/t46vg6_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/t46vg6.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/CombatPragmatist" data-video-tropename="Combat Pragmatist" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Anime/MobileSuitGundamIronBloodedOrphans" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/t46vg6.jpg">
