<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Barbatos Doesn't Give Up Yet.</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Despite being half-dead, down one arm, and falling apart: Mikazuki Augus and ASW-G-08 Gundam Barbatos Lupus Rex reminds the soldiers of Gjallarhorn one last time why he is known as &quot;The Devil of Tekkadan&quot;.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="fv95r2">
